title: Quarkus 1.9.2.Final released - Bugfixes
content: Just a week after 1.9.1.Final, here comes 1.9.2.Final with some bugfixes and documentation improvements. Thanks a lot to everyone providing feedback and pull requests! It is a safe upgrade for everyone using Quarkus 1.9. If you are not using 1.9 already, please refer to the 1.9 migration guide. Whatâ€™s new?...
